I will remain confident in the LORD our GOD. My friends, no one is unreachable when it comes to seeking JESUS' love, grace, hope, and mercy. Confidence in GOD doesn't mean we need to have everything figured out. Just like being a Christian doesn't mean we won't struggle, it simple means that we won't struggle alone. I will remain confident for His goodness. His mercy endures forever! Have a blessed in JESUS.

Philippians 1:6
6 Being confident of this very thing, that He which hath begun a good work in you will perform it until the day of JESUS CHRIST:
